OL,3,CNHS to roll out Martha's Rule for
OL,4,Cpatients' right to urgent second
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FMore than 100 hospitals are preparing
OL,8,Fto introduce 'Martha's Rule', which
OL,9,Fwould allow a second medical opinion
OL,10,Fif a patient's condition is rapidly
OL,11,Fworsening. Health Correspondent
OL,12,FRebecca Barry reports
OL,14,FThe NHS in England will roll out
OL,15,F'Martha's Rule' from April to give
OL,16,Fpatients and families access to a
OL,17,Frapid review if they are .
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/15
