OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News, Merope said:
OL,8,F"Everyone just reassured us that this
OL,9,Fwas normal, and even when I expressed
OL,10,Fmy doubts to the nurse when she had a
OL,11,Frash - which is a really serious sign
OL,12,F- the nurse said trust the doctors,
OL,13,Fthey know what they're doing".
OL,15,FThe pair have since campaigned for
OL,16,FMartha's Rule to be introduced to give
OL,17,Ffamilies more say.
