OL,3,CNHS to roll out Martha's Rule for
OL,4,Cpatients' right to urgent second
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FThe pair hope the system will give
OL,8,Fpatients more power, encourage medical
OL,9,Fprofessionals to listen to those they
OL,10,Fare treating and to normalise the idea
OL,11,Fthat doctors should welcome being
OL,12,Fchallenged.
OL,14,FMerope told ITV News: "When I had
OL,15,Ffriends or family members who went
OL,16,Finto hospital after Martha died, I'd
OL,17,Fsay "if you ever feel anything is
OL,18,Fgoing wrong, do what I didn't do -
OL,19,Fscream the ward down". But now you
OL,20,Fdon't need to, just use Martha's rule."
