OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FThe described Martha as fun and
OL,8,Fdetermined, "with a vast appetite for
OL,9,Flife".
OL,11,F"We'll never know what she would have
OL,12,Fachieved with all her talents."
OL,14,FMartha was being looked after at
OL,15,FKing's after suffering a pancreatic
OL,16,Finjury following a fall from her bike
OL,17,Fwhile on a family holiday in Wales.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/15
