OL,3,CNHS to roll out Martha's Rule for
OL,4,Cpatients' right to urgent second
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FAn inquest heard there were several
OL,8,Fopportunities to refer Martha to
OL,9,Fintensive care but this did not
OL,10,Fhappen. The trust, which is a
OL,11,Fspecialist national referral centre
OL,12,Ffor children with pancreatic problems,
OL,13,Fhas since apologised for mistakes in
OL,14,FMartha's care.
OL,16,FAt one point, Martha began to bleed
OL,17,Fheavily through a tube inserted into
OL,18,Fher upper arm and through a drainage
OL,19,Ftube.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/15
