OL,3,CNHS to roll out Martha's Rule for
OL,4,Cpatients' right to urgent second
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FRegarding the introduction of Martha's
OL,8,FRule, NHS chief executive Amanda
OL,9,FPritchard said it had the potential to
OL,10,F"save many lives in the future".
OL,12,FShe said: "Hearing about the
OL,13,Fheartbreaking loss of Martha and the
OL,14,Fexperiences of her family has had a
OL,15,Fmajor impact for people right across
OL,16,Fthe country, with parents, patients
OL,17,Fand NHS staff welcoming her parents'
OL,18,Fcall for a simple process to escalate
OL,19,Fconcerns when they can see a loved
OL,20,Fone's condition worsening.
