OL,3,CNHS to roll out Martha's Rule for
OL,4,Cpatients' right to urgent second
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,F"But this rollout is part of an
OL,8,Fimportant shift where the NHS is
OL,9,Flooking to change the relationship ,
OL,10,Fclinicians, patients and their
OL,11,Ffamilies."
OL,13,FThe Royal Berkshire Hospital in
OL,14,FReading introduced a similar programme
OL,15,Fback in 2009 called 'Call for
OL,16,FConcern', which provides 24-hour
OL,17,Faccess to a critical care team.
