OL,3,CNHS to roll out Martha's Rule for
OL,4,Cpatients' right to urgent second
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FThe hospital's Chief Executive Steve
OL,8,FMcManus told ITV News: "I think it has
OL,9,Fsaved lives. It's about being able to
OL,10,Finvolve the patient and their
OL,11,Frelatives in terms of the clinical
OL,12,Fdecision-making and hear their
OL,13,Fconcerns and act on them."
OL,15,FHealth Secretary Victoria Atkins paid
OL,16,Ftribute to Martha's parents and
OL,17,Fdescribed the new rule as a "major
OL,18,Fboost" to patient safety".
